  <h2>What Is the Buqon DINE Table?</h2>
  <p>
    Buqon DINE is a multifunctional outdoor table: garden table, grill, and drink cooler all in one. At its core, it's a patio table that transforms into a sociable charcoal grill table with a grill insert in the center. A table with BBQ grill. How does it work? More on that below.
  </p>
  <p>
    But that's not all. The versatile garden table with integrated grill has yet another feature. There's the option to insert an ice bucket to keep drinks cool right at the table. So you virtually never have to leave the table — neither to keep an eye on the food nor to grab drinks from the fridge.
  </p>

