  <h2>How Does a Garden Table with Built-In Grill Work?</h2>
  <p>
    Unlike a classic freestanding grill, the BBQ grill is integrated directly into the dining table. This presents a special challenge in development and implementation on multiple levels. The <a href="/en/garden-table-conversion/">conversion</a> and handling at home, however, are child's play.
  </p>
  <p>
    A lot happens under the garden table: people cross their legs, stretch them out, dogs and cats walk underneath. The risk of burns is high, which is why the Buqon DINE's charcoal container features a temperature-neutral three-pan system on the outer wall. The fireproof pan inserted into the tabletop is the heart of the table. Here, the charcoal radiates heat exclusively upward. This fire bowl containing the charcoal can also be lifted out completely. In general, inserting, removing, and heating the BBQ grill in the table is very easy thanks to the side handles. Find a <a href="/en/garden-table-conversion/">step-by-step guide</a> here.
  </p>
  <p>
    The grill grate is also flexibly removable and attachable, ensuring thorough and easy cleaning. Additionally, a drip pan ensures that fat from grilling doesn't drip onto the charcoal.
  </p>
  <img src="https://www.buqon.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/gartentisch-mit-grilleinsatz-holz-6-personen-1024x768.jpg" alt="Garden table with grill insert" loading="lazy" />

  <h2>Grilling with Friends: Togetherness at the Center</h2>
  <p>
    With the central grill at the table, the evening with friends becomes truly communal. Grilling regains its original character — sitting around the fire and connecting. No one needs to leave the table, conversations aren't interrupted, and everyone has enough space to prepare their own food.
  </p>
  <p>
    The idea of creating something together also comes to the forefront. Unlike the classic grill in the corner, guests are not served with the Buqon DINE grill table. On the contrary: everyone prepares and eats their food equally and simultaneously.
  </p>

  <h2>Why Choose a Table with Integrated Grill?</h2>

  <h3>No More Space Problems on the Terrace</h3>
  <p>
    Where to put the grill on the patio? Whether it's a large gas grill or a kettle grill, a standalone grill takes up considerable space. This question becomes irrelevant with the Buqon DINE — the grill is already in the table! On the contrary: by using the Buqon DINE table as both a garden table and a grill table, you reclaim that space. This space saving is worth its weight in gold — not just on balconies and terraces, but also in the garden. A herb garden would certainly look great in the freed-up corner.
  </p>
  <img src="https://www.buqon.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/03/gartentisch-set-grill-integriert-multifunktional-1024x768.jpg" alt="Garden table set grill integrated multifunctional" loading="lazy" />

  <h3>Eat Together at the Same Time</h3>
  <p>
    Up to 8 people can sit at this multifunctional outdoor table. Everyone prepares their own food — making the togetherness and conversation the center of both cooking and eating.
  </p>

  <h3>Plenty of Space at the Grill Table</h3>
  <p>
    Space for up to 8 people, not only around the garden table but also at the grill grate. The grill is large enough that everyone gets their fill. After grilling, the pan with the charcoal can simply be lifted out of the table. Buqon DINE then becomes an elegant garden table with plenty of space for desserts.
  </p>

  <h3>Different Doneness Levels? No Problem!</h3>
  <p>
    With the Buqon DINE, everyone is their own grill master. A personal pair of grill tongs gives each person the freedom to choose their food and grill it exactly as long as they like. The intensity of flavor is as unique as the person themselves — and with Buqon DINE, this individuality is effortlessly possible. This also eliminates the constant question of what should go on the grill next. With the central grill at the table, everyone has their own spot by the fire.
  </p>
  <p>
    The integrated grill function of the DINE table thus offers something that has never existed before: eating together in company while enjoying completely different dishes. Everyone, just as they please.
  </p>

  <h3>The Best Grill Grate</h3>
  <p>
    Not just the table itself, but above all the heart of the table: the grill insert and grate feature remarkable qualities. The grill grate was designed and developed so that people at the table aren't exposed to the heat of the coals. After all, the charcoal should only cook the food. Furthermore, the fat produced during grilling doesn't drip into the grill pan and onto the charcoal, but into a separate collection pan. The stainless steel grill grate is durable, stable, and made from food-safe, rust-free stainless steel. By choosing the Buqon DINE table, you're opting for the best grill grate in this segment:
  </p>
  <ul>
    <li>Very long lifespan</li>
    <li>Removable angle inserts</li>
    <li>Dishwasher safe</li>
